{"tid":2128758,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「大三罷」學生被控抗拒警務人員 獲撤控自簽守行為處理","createTime":"2020-07-28T07:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T08:19:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f28d3fb81f90694b2748fa6269f393eb7075afa1","tid":2128758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7465&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=1e898b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7465</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 <br />\n👤楊(17) #答辯 (#1111黃大仙 抗拒警務人員)<br />\n<br />\n案情：2019年11月11日黃大仙區有示威者號召阻塞交通，早上5時開始PW1-4以便裝至區內巡邏。0730時PW1-4駕駛沒有記號的警方車輛駛至牛池灣街市外，當時附近有約60-70名示威者聚集叫口號，佔據行人路及天橋。當中有4-5人由天橋上拋下大型物件，橋下有路人清理物件，雙方發生爭執。有見及此，PW1-4落車，見到當中有人身穿制服(校服?)，戴灰色口罩、單手穿手套，即被告，當時被告與其他人士有爭執(?)，PW1因而展示委任證。此時被告向後退並開始掙扎，PW2-3加入制伏被告不成功，PW4加入以警棍打向被告左大腿一下後PW3正式拘捕被告。至黃大仙警署後，警誡下搜出被告有一長者八達通，被告否認與集結有關。<strong><span class=\"red\">錄影會面下被告保持緘默。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020年2月3日被告拒保候查(俗稱踢保)，PW7其後重新拘捕被告，<strong><span class=\"red\">期間被告保持緘默。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前辯方向律政司申請其他方式處理，是日控方表示同意。<br />\n<br />\n同意案情。被告准自簽2000元，守行為24個月，期間不得干犯任何阻礙公眾地方或公職人員的罪行。"},{"pid":"ead6f303de1f433b304555393b9cdd89110e8951","tid":2128758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cd87841153c46b10808ed2ecbdc12ad03cd771","tid":2128758,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"期間被告保持緘默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb68a15c8c34c5b210109e039bd8d8a05788d5a","tid":2128758,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"抗拒警務人員都係罪？我都好撚抗拒喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a89c22be089bf116de5e7cf577b8d29fe71446","tid":2128758,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cc4CXf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcc4CXf0.png&h=3354bfde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec5591b06cf6889a449b7ab9eb5155ac440af6f3","tid":2128758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cd87841153c46b10808ed2ecbdc12ad03cd771","tid":2128758,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"期間被告保持緘默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb81fcd802d62804a67d35cbdc8f15d6ccac847","tid":2128758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb68a15c8c34c5b210109e039bd8d8a05788d5a","tid":2128758,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"抗拒警務人員都係罪？我都好撚抗拒喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98-%E4%BD%95%E8%AC%82%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E8%25AD%2598-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25AC%2582%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=0cc8f32e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E8%25AD%2598-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25AC%2582%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&h=5f48e840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98-%E4%BD%95%E8%AC%82%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC/</a><br />\n<br />\n一條係第 212 章 《侵害人身罪條例》第 36條(B) 的「襲擊、抗拒或故意阻撓在正當執行職務的任何警務人員或在協助該警務人員的人」；<br />\n<br />\n一條係第 232 章 《警隊條例》第 63 條：「任何人襲擊或抗拒執行職責的警務人員，或協助或煽惑任何人如此襲擊或抗拒，或在被要求協助該執行職責的人員時拒絕協助，或意圖妨礙或拖延達到公正的目的而提供虛假資料，以蓄意誤導或企圖誤導警務人員，循簡易程序定罪後，可處罰款 $5,000 及監禁 6 個月。」；<br />\n<br />\n原則上第 232 章 63 條涵蓋範圍廣泛好多，譬如被要求協助警方執行職責但唔協助，已可能屬犯罪。當然，告唔告得入，真係好視乎個官點睇，尤其認為你有否合理辯解，你有無相應法律義務，警方的要求有否干涉你的個人權利等，譬如警察要求你手機解鎖，你唔解，咁唔會構成阻差辦公。<br />\n<br />\n03 年談立徽案，被告談立徽駕車誤闖禁區，當交通警要求出示駕駛執照時，談立徽將執照擲地，被控阻差辦公，罪名成立。後來談立徽上訴到終院，最終判無罪。<br />\n<br />\n當時終審法院常任法官陳兆愷在判詞指市民有義務對警方執行職務予以協助，不過有些情況可屬例外，包括為了「保持緘默權利；要求警察澄清所為何事，以及要他做甚麼；與警察理論，企圖糾正警察的錯誤；想保護正被警察查問的親友，或給親友意見；另有急事要做。」"},{"pid":"2728dd18d33f7ee1072229c1902e6d1b84ea9fe8","tid":2128758,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb81fcd802d62804a67d35cbdc8f15d6ccac847","tid":2128758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb68a15c8c34c5b210109e039bd8d8a05788d5a","tid":2128758,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:21.000Z","ms